description: Retention of part of the structure of Nos. 2-6 (Garrard House) at semi-basement/ ground floor level/ demolish No. 8 (Sussex House) and erection of part one to five storey building (with semi-basement level parking for 91 cars/ cycle parking/ refuse storage) comprising 26 one bedroom/ 75 two bedroom/ 4 three bedroom flats and single storey detached buildings for biomass boiler.
